metadata.name: V of the Cosmos
metadata.description:
1 of 1 derivative of the amazing Violetta Zironi's NFT collection; Another Life.  
Zoom in to V of the Cosmos, 4000x4000 resolution.  
Thank you, V for being a powerful voice in the NFT space, and pushing not only the art forward but the technology, onboarding and being an awesome person for people to come in, join the fun and creativity, and be eased into a lovely home of Music NFT community.

I love you, V! Thanks for everything you do.

Happy birthday and Peace be the Journey!

Get your own Another Life here: https://opensea.io/collection/another-life-by-violetta-zironi
